Abdomen.
Tergite 1 dark reddish brown, pruinescence white, dense, tergites 2–3 with anterior half dark reddish brown, posterior half pale yellowish brown, pruinescence white dense, tergites 4–8 pale yellowish brown, pruinescence white, dense; dorsal setae white, dense, appressed, lanceolate; lateral setae white, elongate. 

